            YOU EXPRESSLY ASSUME ALL RISKS ASSOCIATED WITH TRAVELING TO OR VISITING ANY LOCATION LISTED ON MICHIGAN SPOTS.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-ink-primary mb-4">8. Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-secondary leading-relaxed">
          These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Michigan, United States. Any disputes shall be resolved in the state or federal courts located in Calhoun County, Michigan.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-ink-primary mb-4">9. Contact Information</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-secondary leading-relaxed">
          For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact:<br />
          <strong>Cozyartz Media Group</strong><br />
          Battle Creek, Michigan<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:legal@michiganspots.com" class="text-lakes-blue hover:underline">legal@michiganspots.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="border-t-2 border-ink-primary pt-8 mt-12">
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-faded text-center">
